description: **Esprima** ([esprima.org](http://esprima.org)) is a high performance, standard-compliant [ECMAScript](http://www.ecma-international.org/publications/standards/Ecma-262.htm) parser written in ECMAScript (also popularly known as [JavaScript](http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/JavaScript>JavaScript)). Esprima is created and maintained by [Ariya Hidayat](http://twitter.com/ariyahidayat), with the help of [many contributors](https://github.com/ariya/esprima/contributors).
name: esprima
